ves a dilema on what to drop.<br>
<br>
I'm a Rejuv/Smite spec with just enough points into enhance to pick up the basic spec buffs. If I stay with that template through the respec, I lose the spec buffs (Enhance drops from 11 to 5). If I leave enhance at 11 then I drop smite from 21. Now, this would be the way to go for grouping. However, given that I'm well behind the pack in levels, I normally solo for xp (my luck with pick up groups is running about 50/50 whether I gain or lose experience). Thus, I need the Smite points to keep working toward more levels.<br>
<br>
I'm leaning toward dropping the spec buffs, but thought I'd ask for some input before hand. That would put me at 30/21/5 Rejuv/Smite/Enhance.<br>
<br>
Any thoughts?<br>
<br>
