<br>
Yes, I'll be giving up the DD spec and the mez, but I find that when grouped I never have time or mana to start smiting anyway. I personally hate soloing so to me thats not a concern. Now that being said, everyone has differn't requirements to have fun. If you solo then this wont be the best template.<br>
<br>
For RA's, the group cleric still needs BoF. The new BoL RA sounds good but I need to know more about it... is it an active RA, is it on a timer and if so what is the time, does it last till the Power runs out, how much healing will it do.<br>
<br>
All in all, the cleric's in DAoC are now becoming more of my traditional idea of what a cleric should be.<br>
