<br>
So, honestly, if it were me, I'd prolly not even use the full respec just to get the new heal now.  Levels still matter in RvR and getting those matters more, at the moment, so I'd spec for efficient leveling till I got to 40 then respec my smite points around to get the heal and any enhance I wanted for better groupage and leave the remainder in smite.  <br>
